What is the best way to follow up an amazing workout or prep for an upcoming one?
Your food.

Healthy in = healthy out.
Easier said than done right?
You don't want to scarfice taste and convience is a major factor as well.

Meet Luvo Foods.
Frozen meals that actually taste good!
I found myself mainly bringing them to work for lunches.
They are portable and easy to prepare and better than convience food options.
There were a few times when I ate these meals at home but typically I was grabbing them to go when I was traveling.

