I actually ate this meal before remembering to take a picture of it. *Gasp!*
But from the picture you can see what the meals look like after being removed from the microwave.
The steamable pouches remind me of popcorn bags as they have a note on them that says "This Side Up!"
If you bring these to work make sure you have a plate to transfer to!

The polenta was amazing. Luvo's millet grits and polenta outshined the mashed potatoe side by far.

